文公下》 — https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/孟子/滕文公下","slug":"聖人","sources":[{"chapter":"公孫丑上","plugin":"wikisource","title":"孟子 · 公孫丑上","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/孟子/公孫丑上","work":"孟子"},{"chapter":"卷五","plugin":"wikisource","title":"文子 · 卷五","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/文子/卷五","work":"文子"},{"chapter":"不苟篇","plugin":"wikisource","title":"荀子 · 不苟篇","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/荀子/不苟篇","work":"荀子"},{"chapter":"滕文公下","plugin":"wikisource","title":"孟子 · 滕文公下","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/孟子/滕文公下","work":"孟子"},{"chapter":"第05篇乘馬","plugin":"wikisource","title":"管子 · 第05篇乘馬","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/管子/第05篇乘馬","work":"管子"}],"status":"ok","summary":"自生民以來，未有孔子。伯夷、伊尹、孔子皆古聖人，而孔子集其大成。","tags":["孟子","大禹","周公","孔子","三聖","部:經","部:經/四書類"],"title":"聖人"}